Package io.github.ai4ci.abm

Interface PersonDemographic

All Superinterfaces:
Serializable
@Immutable public interface PersonDemographic extends Serializable
Represents the demographic information of a Person in the simulation. This immutable value object holds static attributes such as age and spatial location, and provides methods to access these properties. It is designed to be Serializable.
